      <h1 class="font-display font-black text-4xl text-ebony mb-3">Introduction to Harmonium</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-ebony/60 leading-relaxed">Your journey into Indian classical music begins here. In this lesson, you'll learn what a harmonium is, how it works, and make your first sounds.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Lesson Progress -->
    <div class="bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-xl p-4 mb-8 flex items-center justify-between">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
        <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-green-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
